### Seed (Only once)
GET http://localhost:9000/seed

### SignIn as User
POST http://localhost:9000/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@localhost.com",
  "password": "user123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

